                     <interp inst="t18220417-153-person1475" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in White Bear gardens, and was with Freemantle when he bought the model of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-153-person1476">
