            . I am a constable. On the 6th of April, I saw the prisoner in Chiswell-street with the model.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-153-person1477">
                  NICHOLAS 
                  DAWKINS
               <interp inst="t18220417-153-person1477" type="surname" value="DAWKINS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220417-153-person1477" type="given" value="NICHOLAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220417-153-person1477" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. On the 16th of April, I took the prisoner in Lower-street, Islington, and asked if he had any knowledge of the model, he said No.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw it in Rosemary-branch-fields, and took it all through Islington; could find no owner, and offered it for sale.</p>
